'''3C 390.3''' is a broad-line [[radio galaxy]] located in the [[constellation]] [[Draco (constellation)|Draco]]. It is also a [[Seyfert galaxy|Seyfert 1 galaxy]] which is an X-ray source.<ref name=3C390>{{ cite web |title=3CR 390.3 -- Seyfert 1 Galaxy |url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-basic?Ident=3C+390.3&submit=SIMBAD+search }}</ref>
