This is a list of [[software]] that provides an alternative [[graphical user interface]] for [[Microsoft Windows]] [[operating system]]s. The technical term for this interface is a ''[[Shell (computing)|shell]]''. Windows' standard user interface is called [[Windows shell]]; [[Windows 3.0]] and [[Windows 3.1x]] have a different shell, called [[Program Manager]]. The programs in this list do not restyle the Windows shell, but replace it; therefore, they look and function differently, and have different configuration options.

