'''William Liddiard''' is a transport [[truck driver]] based out of [[London]]. He is also at the forefront of Liddiard Wheels, an [[omnidirectional wheel]].<ref>[https://www.inverse.com/article/17727-omni-wheel-william-liddiard-interview Get to Know the Man Behind the Omni Wheel, William Liddiard]</ref> He invented an omni-directional [[tire|tyre]], which can move a vehicle sideways.<ref>[http://www.foxnews.com/leisure/2016/06/30/inventors-omnidirectional-tires-makes-parallel-parking-cinch/ Inventors omnidirectional tires makes parallel parking a cinch]{{dead link|date=November 2018}}{{unreliable source|date=November 2018}}</ref>

